Title: Christina Warren returns to break down the 2025 Octoverse report
Description:
That's right, Film Girl (Christina Warren) is back as a host and she's diving into the biggest news of the week. We're unpacking the annual Octoverse report for 2025, including record-breaking growth (one developer a second!), the rise of India as a developer hub, and a major upset in programming languages.

Read the full report: https://gh.io/octoverse
